Package: monteCarloProportions
Type: Package
Title: Utilities For Running Monte-Carlo Simulations On Proportions
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-05-26
Author: Brent McSharry
Maintainer: Brent McSharry <brentm@adhb.govt.nz>
Description: Currently in Alpha development stage. Run multiple simulations of different trial sizes and different known effect sizes. Summarise the data from these trials.
License: AGPL (>= 3)
Depends: Rcpp (>= 1.0.4), RcppProgress (>= 0.1)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppProgress
Suggests: 
    testthat
